Package: ggpointdensity
Type: Package
Title: ggpointdensity: A cross between a 2D density plot and a scatter plot
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lukas P.M. Kremer, Simon Anders
Maintainer: Lukas P.M. Kremer <L-Kremer@web.de>
Description: A cross between a 2D density plot and a scatter plot,
    implemented as a ggplot2 geom. Points in the scatterplot are 
    colored by the number of neighboring points. This is useful to
    visualize the 2D-distribution of points in case of overplotting.
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  ggplot2
Suggests:
  viridis
